Package storm2013.commands

Class Summary
DoNothing Does exactly what its name suggests
DriveStuff Autonomous movement CommandGroup
EncoderDrive Drives a certain number of wheel rotations based on an encoder.
EncoderTurn Same as EncoderDrive, but it turns rather than drive.
GyroTurn Turns the robot based on the gyro.
LowerTilter Lowers the tilter.
MoveTilter Moves the tilter based on user input as configured in OI
PrintAutonomousMove Prints out values based on teleoperated movement that can be used for an autonomouse.
RaiseTilter Raises the tilter
Shoot Spins up the shooter and spins the tomahawk.
SpinDown Spins down the firing wheel.
SpinTomahawk Spins the tomahawk 1 revolution by using a limit switch.
SpinUp Spins up the firing wheel.
TankDrive Drives the robot
TargetPIDCommand Base for TargetPIDTilt and TargetPIDTurn
TargetPIDTilt Tilts the tilter based on the camera stuff
TargetPIDTurn Turns the robot based on camera values and values from the gyro
WaitUntilFullSpeed Just a DoNothing command that specifically waits until the firing wheel is at the correct speed.
